      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, so you're saying i shouldn't have the wine at the same time as the pill? i thought a little bit of alcohol helps people relax and fall asleep faster. is it really that dangerous if it's just one glass? i don't feel like it would do much more than just make me sleepy maybe??",
